sense to me now.

100
00:05:47,458 --> 00:05:49,958
I don't understand why
anyone would fight over food.

101
00:05:50,041 --> 00:05:52,458
However, I am thrilled to
know that these battles

102
00:05:52,541 --> 00:05:54,666
are giving Oshiroi
inspiration for her novel.

103
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,375
Wait, you're writing
about the brawls?

104
00:05:56,458 --> 00:05:57,041
That's cool.

105
00:05:57,125 --> 00:05:58,250
Well.

106
00:05:58,333 --> 00:05:59,583
[SHIRAUME]
Sorry if I was rude but

107
00:05:59,666 --> 00:06:01,791
I'm concerned about
Oshiroi's well-being.

108
00:06:01,875 --> 00:06:04,375
Promise me you won't
push her too hard.

109
00:06:04,458 --> 00:06:07,333
[YARIZUI] I have no intention
of pressuring anyone.

110
00:06:08,791 --> 00:06:11,083
[SHIRAUME] Well,
in that case, she can stay.

111
00:06:11,625 --> 00:06:12,708
[SHIRAUME] Before I go,

112
00:06:12,791 --> 00:06:14,250
