from the student council.

113
00:06:14,333 --> 00:06:15,708
[SATO] Are you a member?

114
00:06:15,791 --> 00:06:17,916
[SHIRAUME] Would I deliver a
message for them if I wasn't?

115
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,083
[SATO] But we
just had the election.

116
00:06:20,166 --> 00:06:21,625
I thought the results
weren't supposed

117
00:06:21,708 --> 00:06:22,500
to be announced
until this weekend.

118
00:06:22,583 --> 00:06:23,875
I assure you, I will be a

119
00:06:23,958 --> 00:06:25,541
member of the student council.

120
00:06:25,625 --> 00:06:29,166
