sure I always get what I want.

121
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:31,375
[SHIRAUME] Sato and
Oshiroi's applications for the

122
00:06:31,458 --> 00:06:33,791
Half-Price Food Lover's
club are approved.

123
00:06:33,875 --> 00:06:36,000
And now that you have the
minimum of three members,

124
00:06:36,083 --> 00:06:37,583
your organization
will be added to

125
00:06:37,666 --> 00:06:39,250
