approved club list.

126
00:06:39,333 --> 00:06:40,708
[YARIZUI] Thank you.

127
00:06:40,791 --> 00:06:42,541
[SHIRAUME] Very well then,
if you'll please excuse me.

128
00:06:42,625 --> 00:06:44,875
I need to get back to my
trash-collection duties.

129
00:06:44,958 --> 00:06:45,833
Trash-collection?

130
00:06:45,916 --> 00:06:47,083
Each day,
the student council

131
00:06:47,166 --> 00:06:48,958
collects trash around campus.

132
00:06:49,041 --> 00:06:50,333
[SHIRAUME]
Then we dispose of it in

133
00:06:50,416 --> 00:06:52,666
the most efficient way possible.

134
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:53,791
