135
00:06:53,875 --> 00:06:56,291
[Sato cries out]

136
00:06:56,375 --> 00:06:57,416
Don't forget about this stuff!

137
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:58,833
Oh, yeah!

138
00:07:01,250 --> 00:07:02,500
[GIRLS]
One, two.

139
00:07:02,583 --> 00:07:07,333
My uniform!
