140
00:07:07,416 --> 00:07:08,750
[STUDENT COUNCIL GIRL 3A]
Hey, wait!

141
00:07:15,041 --> 00:07:16,208
[YAMAHARA] C'mon.

142
00:07:16,291 --> 00:07:17,666
Do you think I give a crap
about some dumbass

143
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:19,791
who jumped into an incinerator?

144
00:07:19,875 --> 00:07:21,125
I heard that the
Ice Witch has been

145
00:07:21,208 --> 00:07:24,125
lookin' for new Dogs,
and she found two.

146
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:29,125
They're freshmen students
Yo Sato and Hana Oshiroi.

147
00:07:29,208 --> 00:07:31,500
They're both pretty weak
but they've got potential,

148
00:07:31,583 --> 00:07:33,083
so I was thinkin' about asking

149
00:07:33,166 --> 00:07:35,208
