us before they get too strong.

150
00:07:35,291 --> 00:07:37,041
[DANDOU]
Here's a question for ya.

151
00:07:37,125 --> 00:07:38,208
[YAMAHARA] Yeah, Coach?

152
00:07:38,291 --> 00:07:39,958
[DANDOU]
