153
00:07:40,041 --> 00:07:41,875
[YAMAHARA] I dunno, but if
the Ice Witch has her eye

154
00:07:41,958 --> 00:07:44,208
on two Dogs, there's
gotta be something.

155
00:07:44,291 --> 00:07:46,833
[DANDOU] So they've got the
same ranking as you boys?

156
00:07:46,916 --> 00:07:48,958
[YAMAHARA] Basically, yes,
but there's one defining

157
00:07:49,041 --> 00:07:51,041
characteristic that
makes us different.

158
00:07:51,125 --> 00:07:53,166
