159
00:07:53,250 --> 00:07:56,916
[YAMAHARA] We aren't scavengers,
we hunt, Coach Dandou.

160
00:07:58,291 --> 00:08:00,291
[OSHIROI] You jumped head-first
into an incinerator and

161
