of the Hunting Dog Unit.

207
00:09:41,916 --> 00:09:42,958
Okay.

208
00:09:47,041 --> 00:09:49,208
[YAMAHARA] Whatever
you do, stick to the plan.

209
00:09:49,291 --> 00:09:52,000
It sounds crazy but,
trust me, it'll work.

210
00:09:52,083 --> 00:09:53,583
All you've gotta do
is follow our lead,

211
00:09:53,666 --> 00:09:56,625
and you'll go home
with a warm bento tonight.

212
00:10:02,666 --> 00:10:04,458
[SATO] Damn, he's fast!

213
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:11,083
[SATO] It's the
Hunting Dog Unit!

214
00:10:13,041 --> 00:10:14,958
