228
00:10:58,208 --> 00:10:59,541
[YAMAHARA] What's up, Sato?

229
00:10:59,625 --> 00:11:01,458
You're thinkin' about switching
teams now, aren't ya?

230
00:11:01,541 --> 00:11:04,250
[SATO] Well, I dunno.
[OSHIROI] "Switching teams"?

231
00:11:04,333 --> 00:11:06,125
