place at the same time.

239
00:11:28,583 --> 00:11:30,541
Until then,
hold on to the jersey.

240
00:11:30,625 --> 00:11:32,500
It's a good fit on you.

241
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:40,000
[UCHIMOTO] Ben-To!

242
00:11:41,250 --> 00:11:42,458
[KENDO CLUB A] I hate to say it

243
00:11:42,541 --> 00:11:43,791
but I ain't so sure about
the newbs, Captain.

244
00:11:43,875 --> 00:11:45,125
[KENDO CLUB F] Yeah, me too.

245
00:11:45,208 --> 00:11:46,666
They don't seem like
they wanna join up with us.

246
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:48,416
[YAMAHARA] They may
not now but they will.

247
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:50,416
They're not gonna be
able to resist the urge of

248
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:53,041
getting their hands on
a bento every night.

249
00:11:53,125 --> 00:11:55,166
The fact that they're
undecided means we've still

250
00:11:55,250 --> 00:11:57,750
got a good chance of
winning 'em over.

251
00:11:58,541 --> 00:12:00,875
[YARIZUI] Dandou and
the Hunting Dog Unit?

252
00:12:00,958 --> 00:12:02,208
Why'd you go with those guys?

253
00:12:02,291 --> 00:12:04,125
When we went to
the supermarket their leader

254
00:12:04,208 --> 00:12:06,166
asked us if we wanted
to join up with them.

255
00:12:06,250 --> 00:12:07,291
[YARIZUI] And?

256
00:12:07,375 --> 00:12:09,750
[SATO] I told 'em
we'd think about it.

257
00:12:09,833 --> 00:12:11,000
[SATO] They work
together in a way that

258
00:12:11,083 --> 00:12:12,708
makes it super easy
to get bento but--

259
00:12:12,791 --> 00:12:14,875
[OSHIROI ] This is the first
time I've ever gotten one!

260
00:12:14,958 --> 00:12:16,833
[YARIZUI] Congratulations.

261
00:12:16,916 --> 00:12:19,000
[SATO] I was really lookin'
forward to eating mine

262
00:12:19,083 --> 00:12:20,750
but it didn't taste
all that great.

263
00:12:20,833 --> 00:12:21,750
[YARIZUI]
Which one did you get?

264
00:12:21,833 --> 00:12:23,000
The large Cheese Pork

265
00:12:23,083 --> 00:12:24,583
Cutlet Curry Rice
bento from Tokiwa.

266
00:12:24,666 --> 00:12:26,750
[YARIZUI] Come on, that's
one of their specialties.

267
00:12:26,833 --> 00:12:28,666
There's no way it tasted bad.

268
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:30,458
They must've
missed the mark today.

269
00:12:30,541 --> 00:12:31,583
It was just "meh."

270
00:12:31,666 --> 00:12:33,416
[YARIZUI] Seriously?

271
00:12:34,833 --> 00:12:35,833
[YARIZUI]
Oh, I get it now.

272
00:12:35,916 --> 00:12:37,791
You get what?

273
00:12:37,875 --> 00:12:39,708
[YARIZUI] Nothing.
Don't worry about it.

274
00:12:39,791 --> 00:12:43,125
[SATO] Aw, c'mon,
don't leave me hangin'.

275
00:12:43,208 --> 00:12:44,916
[YARIZUI] I remember
back when this club was

276
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,500
first started the
president once said.

277
00:12:47,583 --> 00:12:50,375
"You may like bento now,
but wait until you've

278
00:12:50,458 --> 00:12:53,458
tasted one that you've
earned at half-price."

279
00:12:54,291 --> 00:12:55,875
[YARIZUI] Think about
that the next time you dig

280
00:12:55,958 --> 00:12:59,833
into a bento and you'll
understand what I'm getting at.

281
00:13:02,333 --> 00:13:04,416
[YARIZUI]
Thanks for the meal.

282
00:13:22,708 --> 00:13:24,250
And just what do
you think you're doing?

283
00:13:24,333 --> 00:13:25,708
You've already eaten.

284
00:13:25,791 --> 00:13:27,541
[SATO] Just a little bite?
[YARIZUI] Not gonna happen.

285
00:13:34,333 --> 00:13:36,833
[YARIZUI] Fine,
but you guys owe me.

286
00:13:38,708 --> 00:13:40,875
Okay, ladies first.

287
00:13:41,416 --> 00:13:42,916
Wait, you don't
want me eating

288
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:43,958
from your chopsticks,
do you?

289
00:13:44,041 --> 00:13:45,458
I have no
problem with it.

290
00:13:45,541 --> 00:13:46,666
What, are you worried that I'm

291
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:47,750
gonna give you
cooties or something?

292
00:13:47,833 --> 00:13:51,208
No! I'm sure
you're cootie-free!

293
00:13:54,166 --> 00:13:56,083
It's so yummy!

294
00:13:58,833 --> 00:14:00,750
"Ah,"

295
00:14:07,416 --> 00:14:11,708
That's tasty!
Thanks for lettin' me try it.

296
00:14:19,333 --> 00:14:20,333
[OSHIROI] So what's up?

297
00:14:20,416 --> 00:14:21,958
I can tell something's
bothering you.

298
00:14:22,041 --> 00:14:24,875
[SATO] Listen, I was just
wondering if you'd wanna--

299
00:14:24,958 --> 00:14:28,833
well, if you'd
wanna do it with me.

300
00:14:30,958 --> 00:14:32,208
Wow. Uh.

301
00:14:32,291 --> 00:14:34,500
I really don't know how to
respond to that, Sato.

302
00:14:34,583 --> 00:14:35,875
That didn't come out right!

303
00:14:35,958 --> 00:14:37,375
Uh.

304
00:14:37,458 --> 00:14:39,166
I mean, it's not like I'm
not interested in you at all.

305
00:14:39,583 --> 00:14:43,250
It's just--You're
a cool guy, but I want

306
00:14:43,333 --> 00:14:46,166
my first time to be, well,
special, you know?

307
00:14:46,250 --> 00:14:47,625
With someone I love.

308
00:14:47,708 --> 00:14:49,958
But you can hold my
hand if you want to.

309
00:14:50,541 --> 00:14:52,708
I meant do you wanna join
the Hunting Dog Unit with me?

310
00:14:52,791 --> 00:14:53,916
Wait, what?

311
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,375
But I thought you asked
if I wanted to "do it"

312
00:14:55,458 --> 00:14:57,583
with you--
Ow, quit doing that!

313
00:14:57,666 --> 00:14:58,791
I've gotta
do something to

314
00:14:58,875 --> 00:15:00,666
get your mind out of the gutter.

315
00:15:02,208 --> 00:15:03,458
Is that really necessary?

316
00:15:03,541 --> 00:15:04,625
[OSHIROI] I don't
want your hands to be

317
00:15:04,708 --> 00:15:07,166
covered in germs
and oil from my hair!

318
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,166
[SATO] Got it!

319
00:15:36,416 --> 00:15:38,750
You'd better let go of me!

320
00:15:38,833 --> 00:15:41,083
[OSHIROI] Oh hey, welcome back!

321
00:15:41,708 --> 00:15:43,833
[YARIZUI] I thought you were
gonna be out with Sato.

322
00:15:43,916 --> 00:15:47,166
Nah, I decided not
to go, but I brought dinner.

323
00:15:47,250 --> 00:15:48,791
Cool, then let's eat.

324
00:15:59,125 --> 00:16:02,541
[SATO] You gonna make me go by
myself again tonight, Oshiroi?

325
00:16:02,625 --> 00:16:04,333
Yeah, sorry.

326
00:16:08,166 --> 00:16:10,250
Hey look, I wanna
show you something.

327
00:16:10,333 --> 00:16:12,291
See this laurel wreath seal?

328
00:16:12,375 --> 00:16:14,375
You won't believe how
we ended up with this one.

329
00:16:14,458 --> 00:16:16,791
Our bus broke down in a
blizzard and we had to walk

330
00:16:16,875 --> 00:16:20,125
three miles in the snow
to get to the supermarket.

331
00:16:20,208 --> 00:16:21,458
[OSHIROI] Really?

332
00:16:21,541 --> 00:16:23,458
[YARIZUI] When we finally
got there, ten Wolves

333
00:16:23,541 --> 00:16:25,333
were crowded
around the last bento.

334
00:16:25,416 --> 00:16:27,208
We weren't about to
let them take it from us,

335
00:16:27,291 --> 00:16:30,250
so we challenged them
and a giant fight broke out.

336
00:16:30,625 --> 00:16:33,541
It was such
a spectacular victory.

337
00:16:34,458 --> 00:16:36,625
[OSHIROI] I can't
believe you beat me again.

338
00:16:36,708 --> 00:16:38,500
[YARIZUI] Well, I can't
believe that this was

339
00:16:38,583 --> 00:16:40,833
my twenty- third win in a row.

340
00:16:40,916 --> 00:16:43,333
[SATO] There's no way
you're ever gonna beat her.

341
00:16:43,416 --> 00:16:46,166
She's a pro,
just like I am at Virtua.

342
00:16:47,125 --> 00:16:48,250
What's Virtua?

343
00:16:48,333 --> 00:16:50,541
It's a game.
One of my all-time favorites.

344
00:16:50,625 --> 00:16:53,041
See, it's a fighting game
called Virtua Fighter 2.

345
00:16:53,125 --> 00:16:55,791
The stronger the enemy is,
the more fired up you get.

346
00:16:55,875 --> 00:16:58,375
And you have to gain respect
from the other players.

347
00:16:58,458 --> 00:16:59,750
Once you've won
them over, you'll get a

348
00:16:59,833 --> 00:17:01,666
nickname and that
means you've really made it.

349
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:05,000
But only the
strongest get that far--

350
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:22,125
[OSHIROI] Wait for me!
I'm coming with you!

351
00:17:35,166 --> 00:17:36,333
So I don't suppose
you're ready to

352
00:17:36,416 --> 00:17:38,125
give me an answer
tonight, are ya?

353
00:17:38,208 --> 00:17:39,833
You mean, whether
or not I'm gonna join you

354
00:17:39,916 --> 00:17:41,666
and the Hunting Dog Unit?

355
00:17:41,750 --> 00:17:43,708
[SATO] Well, I've
been thinking about it,

356
00:17:43,791 --> 00:17:46,083
and I'll give you my
answer later on.

357
00:17:46,166 --> 00:17:48,000
In my own way.

358
00:18:10,125 --> 00:18:12,375
Aren't you gonna take one?

359
00:18:19,416 --> 00:18:20,958
[YAMAHARA] What the
hell are you doing?

360
00:18:21,041 --> 00:18:22,916
I'm giving you
my answer, Yamahara.

361
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,250
You make winning easy
but that's too boring.

362
00:18:25,333 --> 00:18:28,208
The game's not rewarding
if there's no challenge.

363
00:18:28,291 --> 00:18:30,166
What's the fun
in fighting for bento if

364
00:18:30,250 --> 00:18:32,375
you can just walk
up and take one?

365
00:18:33,708 --> 00:18:35,208
So here's a
little tip for ya.

366
00:18:35,291 --> 00:18:37,125
Bentos taste better
when you earn them.

367
00:18:37,208 --> 00:18:39,375
I'd rather have one I beat a
Wolf to get, than anything

368
00:18:39,458 --> 00:18:41,958
you and your lackeys
could ever get me.

369
00:18:47,083 --> 00:18:50,125
Oh yeah, I almost forgot
to return your jacket to ya.

370
00:18:50,583 --> 00:18:51,916
Well, now
that that's over,

371
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:55,416
guess I'll be able to
enjoy my bento again!

372
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:58,750
Geez,
I completely forgot

373
00:18:58,833 --> 00:19:01,166
that Hiro-chan's was
closed tonight.

374
00:19:10,375 --> 00:19:11,875
We're the
Hunting Dogs, dammit!

375
00:19:11,958 --> 00:19:13,416
As long as we work together,

376
00:19:13,500 --> 00:19:16,041
we can be victorious
even if we're weak!

377
00:19:18,291 --> 00:19:19,416
[SATO] Whether
there's two or twenty,

378
00:19:19,500 --> 00:19:21,750
I'll take you Dogs down!

379
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:28,916
You did it, Sato!

380
00:19:48,291 --> 00:19:49,916
I got one!

381
00:19:55,208 --> 00:19:56,250
Sato!
Come back!

382
00:19:56,333 --> 00:19:57,416
[DANDOU] Down, boy.

383
00:19:58,708 --> 00:19:59,750
He's got a fire that you
and the other Dogs lack.

384
00:19:59,833 --> 00:20:03,125
That kid has the eyes of a Wolf.

385
00:20:03,208 --> 00:20:05,666
Sato.
Good to know.

386
00:20:10,666 --> 00:20:12,875
[SATO] Be honest with me,
are you really cool with

387
00:20:12,958 --> 00:20:15,958
being in the Half-Price
Food Lovers club?

388
00:20:18,291 --> 00:20:19,500
Y'know Sato...

389
00:20:19,583 --> 00:20:21,291
Ever since I was just a kid,
people have picked

390
00:20:21,375 --> 00:20:23,500
on me for being a
little different.

391
00:20:23,583 --> 00:20:25,000
I used to get bullied
a lot because I'm

392
00:20:25,083 --> 00:20:27,000
a germaphobe
and a bit of an oddball.

393
00:20:27,083 --> 00:20:28,833
But not anymore.

394
00:20:28,916 --> 00:20:31,583
You and Yarizui make me feel
as though I really belong!

395
00:20:31,666 --> 00:20:33,041
And--

396
00:20:33,125 --> 00:20:35,875
I can't tell you how happy I
am that I met both of you!

397
00:20:35,958 --> 00:20:39,541
And that's why, I swear,
I'm truly honored to be

398
00:20:39,625 --> 00:20:42,541
one of the members of the
Half-Price Food Lovers' club.

399
00:20:42,625 --> 00:20:43,875
I didn't know.

400
00:20:43,958 --> 00:20:45,291
[OSHIROI] Come on,
let's go upstairs.

401
00:20:45,375 --> 00:20:48,875
Don't just stand there, Sato.
Yarizui's waiting.

402
00:20:57,416 --> 00:20:59,916
[YARIZUI] It looks like
you put up a good fight.

403
00:21:00,375 --> 00:21:01,875
Lemme
ask you one thing.

404
00:21:01,958 --> 00:21:04,541
What do the half-priced
bento mean to you?

405
00:21:04,625 --> 00:21:06,750
Are they nothing more
than just left-over food?

406
00:21:06,833 --> 00:21:08,166
[SATO] No, ma'am!

407
00:21:08,250 --> 00:21:11,333
[BOTH] No, they're not!
They're so much more than that!

408
00:21:15,333 --> 00:21:17,625
[YARIZUI] Keys to the clubroom.
Hold on to 'em.

409
00:21:17,958 --> 00:21:19,500
[OSHIROI] Yes, ma'am!
[SATO] Yes, ma'am!

410
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:22,125
[ALL] Thanks for the meal!

411
00:21:23,166 --> 00:21:25,291
[SATO] Finally!
A bento that tastes good!

412
00:21:25,375 --> 00:21:28,166
[YARIZUI] You two owe me
a bite of yours, remember?

413
00:21:28,250 --> 00:21:29,166
[SATO] What?

414
00:21:33,916 --> 00:21:36,750
[YARIZUI] Okay, guys,
now we can call it even.

415
00:21:38,041 --> 00:21:40,000
[closing song]

416
00:21:49,125 --> 00:21:51,083
[girl singing in Japanese]

417
00:23:11,125 --> 00:23:12,625
[SHAGA] I challenge you, Sato.

418
00:23:12,708 --> 00:23:15,291
[SATO] Huh?
What're you talkin' about?

419
00:23:15,375 --> 00:23:18,208
And why're you fightin' me
with something so soft?

420
00:23:18,625 --> 00:23:21,958
That didn't hurt at all.
It kinda felt good.

421
00:23:27,625 --> 00:23:29,458
[SATO] No way.
Shaga?

422
00:23:35,375 --> 00:23:38,000
The preview?
Do I have to?

423
00:23:38,083 --> 00:23:39,791
The only reason
I came over here is

424
00:23:39,875 --> 00:23:41,833
'cause I wanna play video games.

425
00:23:42,416 --> 00:23:43,583
Let's finish
our match, Sato!

426
00:23:43,666 --> 00:23:46,208
[SATO] Aw c'mon.
Can't it wait 'til next time?

